## Performance Checklist

Before adding images, verify:
- [ ] Correct dimensions for use case
- [ ] File size within recommended limits
- [ ] Descriptive alt text ready
- [ ] Compressed using optimization tools
- [ ] Tested on mobile network (3G simulation)
- [ ] Multiple angles/views for detail pages

## Mobile-First Guidelines

Priority loading order:
1. **First:** Above-fold images (hero, first products)
2. **Second:** Visible product cards in viewport
3. **Third:** Below-fold images (lazy loaded)

For mobile optimization:
- Reduce file sizes by 20-30% for mobile-specific images
- Use 1:1 aspect ratio for consistent grid layout
- Test on slow network (throttle to 3G in DevTools)
- Ensure images load within 2-3 seconds on mobile

